					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-292708#post-2174351</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-292708/explained-scps#post-2174351</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 08 Dec 2014 00:23:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Bryx</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1786305</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>SCP-EX's are open for anyone to write. However, there is a reason that there aren't more of them. Simply being odd but real isn't quite enough. It needs to have had some reason to have been considered anomalous by the standards of the Foundation or its precursors before science explained it or explained why it didn't exist.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
